23 (b) "Value" means:
24 1. In the case of any deed not a gift, the amount of the full actual
25 consideration[ therefor,] paid or to be paid, including the amount of any
26 lien or liens on the property[thereon]; and
27 2. In the case of a gift, or any deed with nominal consideration or without
