6 ($0.50) for each five hundred dollars ($500)[$500] of value or fraction thereof,
7 which value is declared in the deed upon the privilege of transferring title to real
8 property.
9 (3) (a) If any deed evidencing a transfer of title subject to the tax[ herein] imposed in
